	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Action</strong> - 60 ft. Sphere (300 ft.) - 6th Level (Evocation) - VSM (a small crystal sphere)</p><p><strong>[[/save CON]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li><li><p>The explosion freezes water in the area, creating solid ice that floats if it covers a body of water. A creature swimming in the area is trapped in the ice unless it succeeds on the saving throw.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 cold]]{1d6} for each spell level above 6th.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>The sphere can be placed in a container to be used later. If released, it shatters and produces the same effect.</p></li><li><p>You may also throw the globe up to 40 ft. without it shattering, where it becomes inert until you smash it or it is broken. When destroyed, it releases its freezing burst centered on that point.</p></li></ul>",
